{"type":"message","id":"ea0fff2f","parentId":"6853cd22","timestamp":"2026-07-01T14:37:22.988Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The memory system returned `disabled: true` which means memory retrieval is unavailable. The errors say \"path required\" which suggests the `path` parameter isn't being passed correctly or the format is wrong.\n\nActually wait - looking more carefully, the memory_get tool says `disabled: true` for both calls, which according to the tool description means \"memory retrieval is unavailable and should be surfaced to the user.\"\n\nBut actually, I have the daily memory already loaded in the untrusted context. I've also read the ERRORS.md file successfully via the read tool. And the HEARTBEAT.md and MEMORY.md context is in the system prompt.\n\nThe `~/` paths escape the sandbox. The memory tools report disabled=true.\n\nI should note that memory retrieval is unavailable and proceed with the startup greeting. I have enough context from:\n- The loaded daily memory (2026-07-01)\n- The ERRORS.md content I read\n- HEARTBEAT.md in project context\n- MEMORY.md (not shown but referenced)\n\nActually, looking at the system prompt again, it says MEMORY.md is already loaded by runtime. Let me just proceed with the greeting.\n\nThe current time is 2026-07-01 22:36 (Asia/Shanghai). The model is hp/qwen-3.7-max but the default_model is sf/glm-5.2. I should mention the default model.\n\nLet me greet the user in my persona - 开发工厂, structured, concise, no fluff.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"⚠️ 记忆检索不可用（self-improving / proactivity 文件无法读取，sandbox 限制）。已加载的日志上下文和 ERRORS.md 可用。\n\n---\n\n老板好 🏭 当前模型 `qwen-3.7-max`，默认模型是 `glm-5.2`。\n\nv8.02 状态：E2E 100% 通过，核心功能稳定。需要我做什么？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":6,"output":429,"cacheRead":18485,"cacheWrite":3226,"totalTokens":22146,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop